  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know if you can compare it with something, but in those times, when somebody employed 27 people, it was [INAUDIBLE] it is a rather big business.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, all the time, full time, with-- with my father.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's one of the reasons that I-- I saw my parents rather rarely.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were coming, very late, home, coming at noon to-- to have their lunch for a very short time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were raised almost without parents, during the days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She's much younger, but she-- she began at the same school, yeah.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I told you already, because I have no contact with Poles.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I-- I can't say that I have.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was before the-- shortly before the war break out, and I was already 16.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We have been working [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] more in the regions where the Poles were gathering.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So once upon a time, we met the anti-Semites, and even got some beatings from them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But this were-- was very rare.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the reason was that I-- I wasn't coming, too much, together with Poles.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We have to remember that Cracow was conquered, if I am not mistaken, in three days, four days after the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] almost, I think, a week after the-- the-- the town was occupied by the Germans, they began to-- to fight against Jews and to-- to call out some special orders, how the Jews have to behave.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "From the-- almost from the very first moment, I don't remember if it was a week or two or months, but it was very shortly after they came to Cracow that they made us know that we are something other than the Polish, although the Poles were occupied, like we were.",
      "word_count": 51
    }
  ],
